      "text": [
        "3058 - وَ قَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «لاَ يُضَحَّى إِلاَّ بِمَا يُشْتَرَى فِي اَلْعَشْرِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3058 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said: \"A sacrificial animal should only be purchased during the ten days (of Dhul-Hijjah).\""
        ]
      }
    }
